sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(Electron)
    participant Hub as SignalR Hub<br/>(NeoVLabHub)
    participant JC as JobsController
    participant JQS as JobQueueService
    participant ISS as InputStagingService
    participant CS as CacheService
    participant JQR as JobQueueRepository
    participant ClDB as Cluster DB<br/>(PostgreSQL)
    participant RPGA as RunPodGpuPlatformAdapter
    participant SUP as Go Supervisor<br/>(RunPod pod)
    participant FT as filetransfer.Client
    participant CTC as CacheTransferController
    participant H as Python Handler
    participant ArtSync as ArtifactSyncService
    participant AR as ArtifactRepository

    Note over FE,JQR: Phase A — Job Submission

    FE->>JC: POST /api/jobs {mediaId, jobType, parameters}
    JC->>JQS: EnqueueAsync(jobRecord)
    JQS->>ISS: StageJobInputsAsync(jobId, inputs)
    ISS->>CS: StageAsync(jobId, key, stream)
    CS->>CS: write /data/io-cache/{jobId}/input/{key}
    JQS->>JQR: EnqueueAsync(clusterJobRecord)
    JQR->>ClDB: INSERT job_queue (status='queued')
    JQS->>RPGA: EnsureWarmAsync()
    RPGA->>RPGA: GraphQL: check pod status
    JC-->>FE: 202 Accepted {jobId}
    FE->>Hub: Subscribe to job updates

    Note over SUP,ClDB: Phase B — Worker Claims Job (pull model)

    loop Every 3s (POLL_INTERVAL_SECONDS)
        SUP->>ClDB: claim_next_job()<br/>SELECT ... FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
        ClDB-->>SUP: job record (or none)
        SUP->>ClDB: UPDATE status='assigned',<br/>lease_expires_at=NOW()+10min
    end

    Note over SUP,H: Phase C — Input Download + Processing

    SUP->>ClDB: UPDATE status='running'
    SUP->>ClDB: get_input_manifest(job_id)
    SUP->>FT: Download inputs
    FT->>CTC: GET /api/cache/{jobId}/input/{key}<br/>(via Tailscale)
    CTC-->>FT: binary stream
    FT->>FT: Write to /data/io-cache/{jobId}/input/

    alt Analysis handler (transcription, diarization, etc.)
        SUP->>H: POST http://127.0.0.1:{port}/handle<br/>{input_path, output_dir, job}
        H-->>SUP: result JSON
    else ComfyUI job
        SUP->>SUP: POST /prompt to ComfyUI :8188<br/>Poll /history, download artifacts
    end

    Note over SUP,CTC: Phase D — Output Upload

    SUP->>FT: Upload outputs
    FT->>CTC: PUT /api/cache/{jobId}/output/{key}<br/>(via Tailscale)
    CTC->>CTC: Write to /data/io-cache/{jobId}/output/
    SUP->>ClDB: register_output_artifact (INSERT cache_manifest)
    SUP->>ClDB: UPDATE status='completed'

    Note over ArtSync,AR: Phase E — Artifact Sync

    loop Every 10s (ClusterPollingIntervalSeconds)
        ArtSync->>ClDB: SELECT FROM job_queue WHERE status='completed'
        ArtSync->>ArtSync: File.Copy(io-cache → artifacts/)
        ArtSync->>AR: INSERT job_artifacts (SQLite)
        ArtSync->>Hub: Broadcast job.completed
    end

    Hub-->>FE: SignalR event (job.completed / job.failed)
    FE->>FE: Refresh artifact gallery